title: Next 75 2010s Edition With J.R. Smith  | WHAT’S BURNIN | Showtime Basketball

description:
Another special episode of WHAT'S BURNIN is here! Matt and Stak are joined by special guest, J.R. SMith to unveil another set of players on their Next 75 list, all from the 2010s, including guys like Paul George & Draymond Green. They also preview the NBA Finals matchup.
